name: Recycle on Sterling Silver
description:
Average chain length is 52cm, but you might get 60cm or you might get shorter. If you have a length in mind then let me know and you shall get that length!

Has been sealed really well, and tested in the water and even a swimming pool. Although I still advise you don't get it wet or it may turn into a gremlin, especially after midnight... Well, thats not really true, but water could possibly wreck it... As the Lorax would say "you have been warned"
